      "role": "user",
      "content": "thx. i've noticed sometimes the crust stays really pale even when the oven is hot. is there like a specific reason why it wouldn't react? and does the sugar content in the dough change how much \"magic\" happens during the browning process?",
      "source": "evaluator"
